.PARA
^AS MENTIONED, THE <KLDCP PROGRAM IN THE <PDP-11/40 REPLACES MOST OF
THE FUNCTIONS ACCOMPLISHED FROM THE <KI-10 CONSOLE. 
^THIS DOCUMENT WILL DESCRIBE SEVERAL FUNCTIONS OF INTEREST TO
OPERATIONS AND COMPARE THE <KLDCP OPERATION OR COMMAND WITH THE <KI-10
EQUIVALENT.
.NO FILL
.NO JUST
