'<MC,RN' TO RETURN THE <CTY TO THE MONITOR TO START THE SCAN TYPEOUT.
^NOTIFY YOUR SUPERVISOR OF THE SITUATION.
.NOTE
^THERE MAY BE OTHER PARITY ERROR MESSAGES REFERRING TO THE <PDP-11
OR OTHER PARTS OF THE SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE. FOR ALL OF THESE SITUATIONS
YOU SHOULD GET ^TYMSHARE ^MAINTENANCE HELP IMMEDIATELY.
