^TO SET UP A REMOTE CONSOLE DO THIS:
.SKIP 1
.NO FILL
.NO JUST
^^
        1) MAKE SURE THE DATAPHONE HAS POWER AND IS PROPERLY
           CABLED TO THE PHONE LINE AND PDP-11. IF YOU HAVE
           ANY DOUBT THAT IT IS SETUP CORRECTLY, OBTAIN
           MAINTENANCE ASSISTANCE.
.SKIP 1
        2) PRESS THE RED (OR AUTO) BUTTON ON THE DATAPHONE 
           AND WAIT FOR THE PHONE TO RING.
.SKIP 1
        3) TYPE IN THE KLDCP COMMAND 'J KLINIK'. THE SYSTEM
           SHOULD NOW BE IN REMOTE CONSOLE MODE.
